## required packages
library(treemap)

## import data
load("mrt-2011-2015.RData")

## descriptions
nrow(mrt)
## [1] 537807
range(mrt$age)
## [1]   0 117
table(mrt$year)
## 
##   2011   2012   2013   2014   2015 
## 104247 109034 109295 104723 110508
## years of life lost / Belgium
treemap(subset(mrt, year == 2015 & cause3 != "Garbage code"),
        index = c("cause1", "cause2", "cause3"),
        vSize = "YLL")

## years of life lost / Brussels
treemap(subset(mrt, year == 2015 & cause3 != "Garbage code" & region == "BR"),
        index = c("cause1", "cause2", "cause3"),
        vSize = "YLL")

## years of life lost / Flanders
treemap(subset(mrt, year == 2015 & cause3 != "Garbage code" & region == "FL"),
        index = c("cause1", "cause2", "cause3"),
        vSize = "YLL")

## years of life lost / Wallonia
treemap(subset(mrt, year == 2015 & cause3 != "Garbage code" & region == "WA"),
        index = c("cause1", "cause2", "cause3"),
        vSize = "YLL")
